snippet.title: Cats & Dogs: The Revenge of Kitty Galore Nintendo DS Trailer
snippet.description:
505 Games has released the official trailer for Cats & Dogs: The Revenge of Kitty Galore on the Nintendo DS.

To learn more about the game, check out our coverage, here: http://friskymongoose.com/505-games-releases-official-trailer-for-cats-dogs-the-revenge-of-kitty-galore/
